message.body: Hey john! Happy birthday! Sorry this is later, I kept forgetting to text you! But happy birthday and I hope you're having a great time in Cali!
Hey Jenny! Thanks for the birthday wishes. I'm having a great time in California! You should drop by sometime too. It's way warmer than Philadelphia. :p
OMG. I can believe it! I'm secretly jealous but I'm glad you're having fun!!!!
Tell akiha I said hello!!! (I also hope I spelled that right!)
Ahhh that's so beautiful! I'm no longer secretly jealous. I'm a green monster!
